{"tid":2238581,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中槍兩少年：不放棄追究警暴","createTime":"2020-10-11T09:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T10:01:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ece66551a448d5e1ac149d8760299488ad20019d","tid":2238581,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:03:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/SUPYJUWKWBEEBN2JVU2LNVOTQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FSUPYJUWKWBEEBN2JVU2LNVOTQQ%2F&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=ea73449b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FSUPYJUWKWBEEBN2JVU2LNVOTQQ%2F&h=973a3e3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/SUPYJUWKWBEEBN2JVU2LNVOTQQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中槍兩少年：不放棄追究警暴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6lJVxGcD0aH_zNKyKyyyIbhwrfM=/1077x757/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OXVM5HP3NBA2XNECAA2JZF6EX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6lJVxGcD0aH_zNKyKyyyIbhwrfM%3D%2F1077x757%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOXVM5HP3NBA2XNECAA2JZF6EX4.jpg&h=7ebc70a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■健仔對鏡頭展示中槍位置，當時子彈碎片離心臟只有三厘米。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】煙硝間，兩名少年的命運就此改變。去年被警察槍傷的少年「健仔」曾志健和「熊仔餅」周柏均，近日接受BBC及德國之聲訪問，談及身心創傷及追究警暴之路。健仔相信，只要堅持，總有未來與希望；熊仔餅則感嘆，看着香港腐化，感到灰心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n健仔：港人要堅持到底<br />\n<br />\n憶起中槍瞬間，健仔形容「世界好似停咗一秒，熱力由心口慢慢滲出嚟」。18歲中五生曾志健去年10月1日在荃灣遭警員實彈射傷，子彈碎片離心臟只有三厘米。與死神擦肩而過的他當時想過會犧牲，對於中槍後仍生存感幸運，但須面對後遺症，如肋骨曾斷裂，不時受神經痛之苦。<br />\n<br />\n人生改變的還有21歲IVE學生周柏均。去年11月11日民間發起三罷，周在西灣河遭交通警實彈射中右腹，須切除右腎和三分之一肝臟。受訪期間周展示疤痕，「對住塊鏡有啲想喊」。他透露生活亦因槍傷劇變，如因愛吃樂天熊仔餅而獲「熊仔餅」稱號的他不能再吃甜食，腸黏裂更令他痛苦難忍，嚴重時要打止痛針。他至今仍經常流淚不止，上學時感不安，在街上看到警察亦會驚慌。康復路漫長，他覺得有點累，「見到（社會）慢慢腐化落去，有啲灰心」。<br />\n<br />\n二人希望追究警暴，周中槍時手無寸鐵，形容雙方武力不對等，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n追究警暴之路困難重重，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n健仔昨在社交媒體指，慶幸能繼續保釋，會珍惜時間完成想做的事，寄語港人「保持健康，有健康的身體，才能夠堅持到底」，他在訪問中談到健康與前途時也相信，只要堅持，總有未來與希望。"},{"pid":"914abe7688739a1dccce8c0564d64ccc01e617b1","tid":2238581,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db04c3d87c7c652189dac667b092ea687c4b901","tid":2238581,"uid":164965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:11:46.000Z","msg":"點解冇其他post講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b19f2bbffa7cc1eb0ab54933d59079a7d8d177e","tid":2238581,"uid":240004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:16:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"abded171e15cf7af120089305ec1e7aa81808de6","tid":2238581,"uid":181697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:16:13.000Z","msg":"死警畜 開槍易 對普通市民既傷害有幾大<br />\n支持手足告警畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba08a7c76b868f2c275647d81f4c4d8dba4ce79b","tid":2238581,"uid":240004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"好堅強<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8908615477a84ed75032548c5fa11d218a262d89","tid":2238581,"uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"元朗中溜彈𠴱位巴打依加點？"},{"pid":"ec670693afb4717de57e37df4ebac3be49a2cba7","tid":2238581,"uid":8948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:21:56.000Z","msg":"仲有天水圍係天台向下射催淚彈打中人個頭"},{"pid":"600d875c4f2e8710643eda4fb593dc05f28eea03","tid":2238581,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:22:59.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"4cfd0254985075cc1c3283e38a095a36498b0534","tid":2238581,"u